cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "usqldb: PostgreSQL 17-compatible layer for UQA --- system catalogs, CLI, and wire protocol server"
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
authors:
  - given-names: Jaepil
    family-names: Jeong
