license: AGPL-3.0-only
version: 0.2.0
date-released: "2026-04-05"
abstract: >-
  PostgreSQL 17-compatible layer for UQA providing system catalogs,
  a psql-style CLI, and a wire protocol server with query cancellation,
  enabling standard PostgreSQL clients to connect to and introspect
  UQA databases.
keywords:
  - postgresql
  - information-schema
  - pg-catalog
